    <caption>Normal sea surface temperatures (SSTs) in the equatorial Pacific (for the period 1961-1990). This figure is identical to <xref ref="fig_sst_map">Figure</xref>, except for its focus on the Pacific and the different color scale. The
    <q>Western Pacific Warm Pool,</q>
